<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="swear-v">swear <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sweə(r)/    美 /swer/  </p>
<p>(swore, sworn)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>诅咒；咒骂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>swear at</strong> sb 
咒骂某人</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>宣誓；发誓：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>swear to God</strong> 
向上帝发誓</p></div>

<ul>
<li>swear to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you swear to tell the truth, the whole truth, and nothing but the truth? 
你能发誓据实陈述而决无谎言吗？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>swear +(that)从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She swore (that) she’d never seen him before. 
她发誓说以前从没见过他。</p></div></div>